[[!template id=stub]]The **remote miner** (1.1) is an open source Bitcoin [[pooled miner|Pooled_Mining]] created by puddinpop. 

It communicates through a JSON-based protocol, and supports mining via [[CPU|Cpu_Miner]] and GPU ([[OpenCL|OpenCL_miner]] and CUDA).

